IMAPStore general-remote
Host mail.aryadevchavali.com
Port 993
User aryadev
PassCmd "pass mutt-wizard-general"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore general-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/general/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/general/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel general
Expunge Both
Far :general-remote:
Near :general-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile
